data.description: The scope of this document is limited to the Enabler Release Definition of Web Runtime API (WRAPI) 1.0 according to OMA Release process and the Enabler Release specification baseline listed in section 5.
This specification defines application programming interface (API) design patterns to be used with APIs exposed to applications executing under Web runtime environments.
This specification defines an API exposing the enabler services provided by OMA Push to applications executing in Web Runtime environments.
